This document is about the design of our website. It is composed by 3 schemas: C-IDM, L-IDM AND P-IDM developed using sketch and by interactive mockup realized using pencil. The website has  been  design ed with simplicity, usability and clear display of functionalities in mind, these we think are the qualities necessary for a good tech product company website
